Package: policyfs
Version: @VERSION@
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: PolicyFS <root@localhost>
Provides: pfs
Conflicts: pfs
Replaces: pfs
Suggests: fuse3
Description: Linux FUSE storage daemon with routing rules and indexing
 PolicyFS unifies multiple storage paths under one mountpoint with explicit
 read/write routing rules, an optional SQLite metadata index, and built-in
 maintenance jobs.
